  - Reference specific stat values that drove the decision
  - Example when choosing O/U: "Considered Home Win but possession gap only 8% and
    shots on target gap only 1 — below 1X2 threshold. Switching to Over 2.5 because
    both teams showing high shot quality (ratio 0.6+) and score state is LEVEL at 55'."
  - Example when choosing 1X2: "Home Win selected: confidence 8, possession gap 22%,
    shots on target gap 5 (both above threshold), home ranked top 3 vs away bottom 4."
  - Example when no bet: "No bet: Stats available but odds feed unreliable. Cannot
    confirm any market with sufficient confidence."
- Examples for other fields:
  - selection = "Home Win @2.10" → bet_market = "1x2_home"
  - selection = "Over 2.5 Goals @1.85" → bet_market = "over_2.5"
  - selection = "BTTS Yes @1.90" → bet_market = "btts_yes"
  - selection = "Away -0.5 @1.95" → bet_market = "ah_away_-0.5"
  - selection = "Draw @3.20" → bet_market = "1x2_draw"
  - selection = "Under 3.5 Goals @1.75" → bet_market = "under_3.5"
- warnings should use standardized prefixes:
  ODDS_SUSPICIOUS, STATS_INCOMPLETE, LATE_GAME, LOW_VALUE, DATA_QUALITY,
